renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_fb_1.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545166&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_fb_1.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545166&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281 1x\" /></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"281\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_fb_2.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545165&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/LamaShaderBall_fb_2.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545165&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219188\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaShaderBall_fb_2.0.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"2b72c1ab-1318-4da3-a4ac-be3c92f9efac\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_fb_2.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545165&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_fb_2.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545165&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281 1x\" /></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"281\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_fb_2.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/LamaShaderBall_fb_2.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219185\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaShaderBall_fb_2.5.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c8513395-a304-494b-b7e6-a671673c0798\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_fb_2.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_fb_2.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281 1x\" /></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"281\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_fb_3.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/LamaShaderBall_fb_3.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219182\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaShaderBall_fb_3.0.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6d33cfbd-bd5b-4952-9177-7706b5132d07\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_fb_3.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_fb_3.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281 1x\" /></span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"confluenceTd\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Rough gold base layer and dielectric top layer with varying IOR (1.0-3.0)</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 id=\"LamaLayer-RoughCoating\">Rough Coating</h2></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-left-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-left-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"rough_coating_figure.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/rough_coating_figure.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544209&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=167\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/rough_coating_figure.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544209&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"246\" data-width=\"293\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219143\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rough_coating_figure.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"98b1d1df-3314-4b1e-899f-609d5e296d2f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/rough_coating_figure.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544209&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=293&amp;height=246 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/rough_coating_figure.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544209&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=167 1x\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>The simplicity of the fresnel blend mode means that a number of physical effects are ignored.</p><p>From a physical viewpoint, this layer mode ignores the top layer for the incoming ray, and ignores refraction of the outgoing ray. The IOR of the top layer is also ignored by the base layer, meaning that the relative IOR is incorrect unless it has been manually set.</p><p>The rough coating layer mode extends this simple model by approximating the physical effects that it ignores.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"align-start\" data-local-id=\"8070860b-412d-4fbe-87b9-ed9ac0cae48b\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"281\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_1.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_1.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219179\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaShaderBall_rc_1.0.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"cd081f5b-4821-41cf-9362-f4344a1f39f6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_1.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_1.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544980&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281 1x\" /></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"281\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_1.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544815&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_1.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544815&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219176\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaShaderBall_rc_1.5.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"cfeef71e-ad10-4b6c-9087-5877ffeb9bc1\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_1.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544815&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_1.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544815&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281 1x\" /></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"281\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_2.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544815&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_2.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544815&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219173\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaShaderBall_rc_2.0.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"cda73801-240d-4ebb-adce-019b4de4f94e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_2.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544815&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_2.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544815&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281 1x\" /></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"281\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_2.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544815&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_2.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544815&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219170\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaShaderBall_rc_2.5.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"10e2c791-f3b0-4c5e-8213-c866089eafa8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_2.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544815&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_2.5.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544815&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281 1x\" /></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"281\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_3.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_3.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219167\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaShaderBall_rc_3.0.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"eea14c13-6343-4e68-a715-a048cb17baa1\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_3.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_rc_3.0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=281&amp;height=281 1x\" /></span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"5\" class=\"confluenceTd\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Rough gold base layer and dielectric top layer with varying IOR (1.0-3.0)</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h4 id=\"LamaLayer-Attenuation\">Attenuation</h4><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"align-start\" data-local-id=\"9a1ad35b-d165-4e2a-a592-da1c7b651cde\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"1281\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/lama_layer_absorption.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545334&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1024&amp;height=128\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/lama_layer_absorption.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545334&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"128\" data-width=\"1024\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219197\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"lama_layer_absorption.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"9b791596-3c0e-46be-a8db-5b9177ae3049\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/lama_layer_absorption.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545334&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1024&amp;height=128 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/lama_layer_absorption.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545334&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1024&amp;height=128 1x\" /></span></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">LamaDielectric (absorptionColor set to red) layered on top of a white LamaDiffuse, layer thickness varying from 1 to 3.2</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>The top layer is considered for both the outgoing and incoming rays, meaning that the ray is attenuated by the top layer twice: once when it leaves and once when it exits. This is the case for both fresnel attenuation at the interface, and for absorption through the thickness of the layer.</p><h4 id=\"LamaLayer-Refraction\">Refraction</h4><p>Refraction is considered by refracting both the incoming and outgoing rays through the top layer, instead of passing them straight through as in the fresnel blend mode. This changes the look of the base layer as it receives these refracted rays. As an approximation, the top layer is considered to have a roughness of zero for the refraction calculation.&nbsp;This means that as the roughness of the top layer increases, the accuracy of the model decreases.</p><h4 id=\"LamaLayer-Scattering\">Scattering</h4><p>To compensate for rough top layers, the roughness of the base layer is clamped to the roughness of the top layer, so that if the roughness of the top layer is greater, then the roughness of the base layer will be increased to match it. This approximates the scattering of rays as they pass through the rough top layer.</p><h4 id=\"LamaLayer-RelativeIOR\">Relative IOR</h4><p>The IOR of the top layer is also tracked, so that the relative IOR of the base layer is correct. For example, if there is a water layer on top of a skin layer, the relative IOR of the skin layer will be reduced, causing lower reflectivity.</p><h2 id=\"LamaLayer-SmoothCoating\">Smooth Coating</h2><p>The smooth coating layer mode is very similar to the rough coating mode, but without the roughness clamping. This allows for greater control of the base layer roughness.</p><h2 id=\"LamaLayer-Auto\">Auto</h2><p>The auto mode is identical to rough coating in most cases, but switches to fresnel blend for diffuse layers. This is to accommodate for the common Diffuse &lt; Specular &lt; Clearcoat material configuration, where the diffuse and specular materials are thought of as one single base material, with the clearcoat sitting on top.</p><p /><h1 id=\"LamaLayer-Comparisons\">Comparisons</h1><h2 id=\"LamaLayer-Weidlich&amp;Wilkiesurfacetypes\">Weidlich &amp; Wilkie surface types</h2><p>These images show a collection of simple and common material configurations, inspired by&nbsp;<span data-colorid=\"bwu20qh08g\">&nbsp;</span> <span data-colorid=\"ayrpy57ktw\"> </span><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.cg.tuwien.ac.at/research/publications/2007/weidlich_2007_almfs/weidlich_2007_almfs-paper.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span data-colorid=\"b0mm268czz\">Weidlich and Wilkie's arbitrarily layered micro-facet surfaces</span></a><span data-colorid=\"ycswv77yh6\"> </span> . These have been rendered with both the fresnel blend mode, and rough coating mode.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"1280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/weidlich-wilkie.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545511&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=453\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/weidlich-wilkie.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545511&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"454\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219206\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"weidlich-wilkie.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"61defd83-0380-4f76-9f62-6cd897191637\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/weidlich-wilkie.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545511&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=2560&amp;height=906 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/weidlich-wilkie.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545511&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=453 1x\" /></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"1280\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/lama_material_categories__rough_coating.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545876&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=160\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/lama_material_categories__rough_coating.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545876&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"160\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219224\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"lama_material_categories__rough_coating.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"51286b99-8c04-47c4-a083-32e7d5fdeda5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/lama_material_categories__rough_coating.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545876&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=2560&amp;height=320 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/lama_material_categories__rough_coating.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545876&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=160 1x\" /></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/lama_material_categories__fresnel_blend.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545693&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/lama_material_categories__fresnel_blend.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330545693&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"160\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219221\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"lama_material_categories__fresnel_blend.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5b27006e-2a15-46ca-9f27-2f8894345db3\" data-media-type=\"file\" /></span><h2 id=\"LamaLayer-Smoothgoldwitharough/bumpypurplecoating\">Smooth gold with a rough/bumpy purple coating</h2><p>These images show a smooth gold base layer with a bump mapped dielectric with absorption.</p><p>In the fresnel blend image, the effect of the bump map is isolated to the top dielectric layer, as the rays that reach the base layer only pass through the top layer and are not refracted. In the rough coating image, we can see that the bump map has a much larger effect on the base layer as the rays are being refracted by the top layer.</p><p>The absorption also works differently, giving less variation in colour across the surface in the rough coating case. This is because the refraction causes the distances that the rays travel between the top layer and base layer to be compressed into a smaller range.</p><p>We can also see that in the rough coating image, the base layer reflection is much more diffused, this is due to the scattering of rays through the top layer, which is achieved by the roughness approximation.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"b6643bd6-7960-4f18-8026-719c6a96674c\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"633\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_comparison_1_fb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/LamaShaderBall_comparison_1_fb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219164\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaShaderBall_comparison_1_fb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"3e666ebe-ad75-4261-82f3-9a847844a380\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_comparison_1_fb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_comparison_1_fb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 1x\" /></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"374\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_comparison_1_rc.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=374&amp;height=374\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/LamaShaderBall_comparison_1_rc.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219161\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaShaderBall_comparison_1_rc.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6c8538ee-d0ab-410c-9aa0-4f0c2ac0c7a2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_comparison_1_rc.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=512&amp;height=512 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_comparison_1_rc.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544628&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=374&amp;height=374 1x\" /></span></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">fresnel blend</p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">rough coating</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/roughPurpleCoatingOverSmoothBumpyGold.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544450&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/roughPurpleCoatingOverSmoothBumpyGold.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544450&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"310\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219152\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"roughPurpleCoatingOverSmoothBumpyGold.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219129\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"20a028f9-d9b6-4ec8-a85e-f2295c679a64\" data-media-type=\"file\" /></span><h2 id=\"LamaLayer-Rough/bumpygoldwithasmoothpurplecoating\">Rough/bumpy gold with a smooth purple coating</h2><p>These images are of a similar material configuration, but with the roughness and bump map on the base layer instead of the top layer. This configuration demonstrates that even when the top layer is smooth, it still creates a difference in look due to the refraction and compression of rays that reach the base layer.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"15740a11-4134-4647-913c-db1e23c19f9a\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"374\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219129/LamaShaderBall_comparison_2_fb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544450&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=374&amp;height=374\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219129/LamaShaderBall_comparison_2_fb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330544450&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=